rows.label: qst201611_msg0001
rows.name:
Bravo! Bravo!
Success that resound!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0002
rows.name:
Pi knew friend Nanakoori can do it!
Entire audience under friend's spell!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0003
rows.name: How did it feel, Nanakoori?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0004
rows.name: ...Mm. It felt really good!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0005
rows.name:
When I was singing, I felt like I was
a part of something bigger than myself!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0006
rows.name: That sounds great!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0007
rows.name: To tell truth, Tora feel that way too...!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0008
rows.name:
What the heck have you got to
cry about?!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0009
rows.name:
After this concert, fame of friend Nanakoori
go through roof!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0010
rows.name:
Next time, me able to bring
voice of Nanakoori to even bigger
masses, book even bigger stage!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0011
rows.name: Where is there a bigger stage?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0012
rows.name: Alba Margen, meh!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0013
rows.name: Huh?!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0014
rows.name:
Alba Margen? As in,
the capital of Superbia?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0015
rows.name:
Exactamundo!
One and the same, meh.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0016
rows.name:
Playing in the capital, huh...?
I can't even imagine the crowd...

rows.label: qst201611_msg0017
rows.name:
Nobody ever try to play concert
in Alba Margen before.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0018
rows.name:
If we succeed at holding concert
of this magnitude, friend Nanakoori be
star likes of which world never see!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0020
rows.name: Bit of a scary thought, eh?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0021
rows.name:
...Yes.
A lot scary, even.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0022
rows.name:
But...I still want to try.
It seems a lot of people are interested
in hearing me sing, after all.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0023
rows.name:
Yes yes, that the spirit!
With that attitude, success is
guaranteed!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0024
rows.name:
...Ah, but to fill venue in Empire,
friend Nanakoori will
need even more fans.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0025
rows.name: How many exactly?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0026
rows.name:
By estimate of Pi,
upwards of five thousand or so.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0027
rows.name:
How many?!
That's daft!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0028
rows.name:
Not at all!
Friend Nanakoori have no problem
in getting required numbers!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0029
rows.name:
Yes!
I'll do my best!
